{"tid":255652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回歸20年】舞照跳嗎？","createTime":"2017-05-24T03:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T03:51:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cba0e275351a78a3077a9ef6ffb0661e1c6ab410","tid":255652,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20032178&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20032178%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170524&d=Kip4ldzm97COJiwa4u3YGjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8423c690\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20032178%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170524&h=5221924a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20032178&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170524</a><br />\n<br />\n【回歸20年】舞照跳嗎？<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n至今夜總會由大場變中小型，根據酒牌局資料顯示，目前全港只剩49間，而當中日式夜總會更僅存俏佳人、富都及侯爵會3間，今非昔比。取而代之的是，近年猶如雨後春筍的私人會所，2007年廣播處前處長朱培慶被揭幫襯會所後帶女伴出街，標誌會所遍地開花，會所經營者文哥笑言：「梗有一間喺左近！」<br />\n時至今日，夜總會變會所，D場變為Clubbing場，見證娛樂事業興衰、當年紅爆D場的《老豆咪索茄》填詞人DJ Lorry，對香港是否仍「舞照跳」幽了一默：「舞係照跳，不過係跳大媽舞，廣場舞！」<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n廣場舞近年殺入香港，公園等地早晚可見大媽「芳蹤」。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=Kip4ldzm97COJiwa4u3YGjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0811fbd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n昔日豪客邊行邊派金牛<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n玩家：點解唔返內地玩<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【動畫‧舞照跳】泊車仔80年代月入逾萬<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【舞照跳】會所本小利大　撼低夜總會<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n回到英殖時︰李國能任首位終院首席法官<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n回歸百科︰【中英聯合聲明】<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n夜場起落如香港興衰「舞係照跳　但係大媽跳」<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"18d61306f0fdce42218ddb89606e413cab41b337","tid":255652,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"廣場舞近年殺入香港，公園等地早晚可見大媽「芳蹤」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170524/large/24aa9p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F24aa9p5.jpg&h=67eb96d3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}